videos.headline: Thorson converts on fourth down
videos.description: Quarterback Clayton Thorson scrambles to give Northwestern a first down.

videos.headline: Thorson runs it in for Northwestern score
videos.description: QB Clayton Thorson uses his legs to put the Wildcats on the board.

videos.headline: Purdue runs fake punt to perfection
videos.description: Punter Joe Schopper throws a dime up to long snapper Ben Makowski who hauls it in despite a vicious hit.

videos.headline: Purdue stuffed on 4th down from the 4-yard line
videos.description: Richie Worship was swallowed up by the Northwestern defense on fourth down deep in the red zone.

videos.headline: Skowronek high-points it for TD catch
videos.description: Bennett Skowronek goes Randy Moss on Purdue cornerback Josh Okonye in the corner of the end zone for the score.

videos.headline: Northwestern's Fitzgerald likes how his offense looks
videos.description: Head coach Pat FItzgerald says QB Clayton Thorson is getting the ball out quick.

videos.headline: Sindelar throws a strike for TD
videos.description: Elijah Sindelar rips a perfect pass to Jarrett Burgess for the Purdue touchdown.

videos.headline: Mahoungou dives in for Purdue TD
videos.description: Anthony Mahoungou stretches inside the pylon to cut the Purdue deficit to 10.

videos.headline: McShepard picks it off to ice the game for Northwestern
videos.description: Marcus McShepard catches tipped ball to seal the win over Purdue.

videos.headline: Fitzgerald proud of a 'good team win'
videos.description: Northwestern head coach Pat Fitzgerald is happy that his team finally won in regulation, after three straight OT games.

videos.headline: Northwestern wins the game through the air
videos.description: Beth Mowins and Anthony Becht say QB Clayton Thorson's efficiency through the air was the key to the win.
